<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.2">
<l>maṟantēṉuṉ ṉaimuṉṉam maṟantamati yiṉmaṉattāl</l>
<l>iṟantēṉet taṉaiyu mataṉāliṭum paikkuḻiyil</l>
<l>piṟantēyeyt toḻintēṉ perumāṉtiru mārpā</l>
<l>ciṟantēṉniṉ ṉaṭikkē tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I neglected you before with a mind with no knowledge of negligence.</l>
<l>I died untold [times]; therefore, having been [re]born into a pit of suffering,</l>
<l>Being weary, I gave up. Great lord, one with Tiru at your chest,</l>
<l>I triumphed only at your feet, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
